title: Derek Carr’s Extension and Ultimate War Room Draft
description:
Kevin, Nora, and Kaelen react to the news of Derek Carr’s extension, Baker Mayfield’s interview, and Brady’s potential ownership with the Miami Dolphins. The trio is later joined by Rodger Sherman to pick their ultimate war room for the NFL draft.

Host: Kevin Clark, Nora Princiotti, and Kaelen Jones 
Guest: Rodger Sherman
Associate Producer: Stefan Anderson
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
